        def _dfs(curr: int, visited: Set[int], next: List[int]):
            visited.add(curr)
            for nxt in next:
                if nxt not in visited:
                    _dfs(nxt, visited, edges[nxt])

        for i in range(N):
            if i in visited:
                continue
            next = edges[i]
            _dfs(i, visited, next)
        return 'POSSIBLE' if len(visited) == N else 'IMPOSSIBLE'
    return ''
